♪ Oh, dancing with myself♪

08:04.568 --> 08:07.862
♪ Oh, there's nothing to lose
and there's nothing to prove ♪

08:07.946 --> 08:10.239
♪ And I'll be
dancing with myself♪♪

08:14.953 --> 08:15.953
- [School Bell Rings]
- I have something
I'd like to say.

08:15.954 --> 08:17.413
- [School Bell Rings]
- I have something
I'd like to say.

08:19.374 --> 08:21.917
I wanna audition
for the Wicked solo.

08:22.002 --> 08:24.545
- [Murmuring]
- Kurt, there's a high "F"
in it.

08:24.629 --> 08:27.006
That's well
within my range.
[Tittering]

08:27.090 --> 08:31.051
Well, I think Rachel's
gonna be fine
for the female lead.

08:31.136 --> 08:33.053
But I'm happy to have you
try out something else, Kurt.

08:33.138 --> 08:35.431
- And we'll make sure that
it's got a killer high note.
- [Murmuring]

08:35.515 --> 08:37.850
You tried.
Anyway,

08:37.934 --> 08:40.060
I wanted to say
something to you guys.

08:40.145 --> 08:43.981
I was a little disappointed
at how you were all
so willing...

08:44.065 --> 08:45.983
to take the bus together
to sectionals...

08:46.067 --> 08:49.320
and make Artie
drive by himself with his dad.

08:49.404 --> 08:53.240
We're a team, guys.
We're in this
Glee Club together.

08:53.325 --> 08:56.076
Artie doesn't care.
His dad drives him everywhere.

08:56.161 --> 08:59.788
I do care.
That kind of hurt
my feelings.

08:59.873 --> 09:01.457
We didn't think you would
take it personally.

09:01.541 --> 09:06.879
Well, you're irritating
most of the time, but
don't take that personally.

09:06.963 --> 09:09.006
I don't know if you guys
really understand
how much harder...

09:09.090 --> 09:11.342
- Artie has to work
just to keep up.
- Preach.

09:11.426 --> 09:14.220
We're riding
to sectionals together,

09:14.304 --> 09:16.222
or we're not going at all.

09:16.306 --> 09:19.558
And to pay for the bus,
we're having a bake sale.

09:19.643 --> 09:24.563
- [Boy] Bake sale.
- St. Ignatius nursing home
was having a tag sale.

09:24.648 --> 09:28.150
And my A.V. Club friends here
agreed to help out.

09:30.237 --> 09:33.656
For the next week,
each of you is going to spend...

09:33.740 --> 09:36.617
three hours a day
in a wheelchair.

09:38.119 --> 09:41.997
Oh, oh, oh.
And we're doing
a wheelchair number.

09:42.082 --> 09:44.291
[Artie Clapping Softly]

09:46.878 --> 09:49.088
♪♪ [Rock]

09:49.214 --> 09:51.757
♪ On the floors of Tokyo ♪
Oh!

09:51.841 --> 09:54.927
♪ Or down in London town
to go, go ♪

09:55.011 --> 09:57.137
♪ With the record selection
and the mirror's reflection ♪

